Titolo: Valis: The Fantasm Soldier

Anno: 1986

Descrizione: Valis: The Fantasm Soldier is a platform game developed by Wolf Team and published by Telenet Japan in 1986 originally for the PC-88 and MSX home computers. It is the first video game in the Valis series which stars a Japanese teenager named Yuko who uses a mystical sword called Valis to defend Earth and other worlds.
Since release, it has been ported, remade, or re-released for several other systems. Its critical reception has varied depending on the version, including critical acclaim for the 1992 PC Engine remake.